sourcesContent: import React from "react"; import {MDBBtn,MDBTable,MDBTableBody,} from "mdb-react-ui-kit"; import ListGroup from 'react-bootstrap/ListGroup'; const Filter = (props) => { let i=0 const finish=(e)=>{ e.preventDefault() props.todos.isDone==='Done' } return ( <> { props.searchfilter==='isDone' ? props.todos.filter((todo) => { todo.isDone === true; }) .map((todo) => ( {i+1} {todo.description} Complete Delete ) ) : props.searchfilter === "Not-Yet" ? props.todos .filter((todo) => { return todo.isDone === false; }) .map((todo) => ( {i+1} {todo.description} In progress Delete Finished )) : props.todos.map((todo, i) => ( {i+1} {todo.description} In progress Delete Finished )) } ); } export default Filter;
